OL,3,CThief guilty of murdering 'kind' man
OL,4,Cwho died in house fire
OL,6,FA thief who killed a man in his own
OL,7,Fhome and stole his television has been
OL,8,Ffound guilty of murder.
OL,10,FWilliam Joyce, 38, attacked Darren
OL,11,FLeach at his house on Marsden Grove in
OL,12,FLeeds in March, likely leaving him
OL,13,Fincapacitated when a fire in the
OL,14,Fbuilding later took hold.
OL,16,FHis body was found by friends the next
OL,17,Fday and a post mortem revealed he had
OL,18,Fburn injuries, seven broken ribs,
OL,19,Fseveral fractures to his larynx and
OL,20,Fbruising to his face and neck. He had
OL,21,Falso inhaled carbon monoxide.
