OL,6,FPolice said they were unable to
OL,7,Festablish if the fire was deliberate
OL,8,For accidental but that Darren was
OL,9,Flikely unable to escape the flames
OL,10,Fbecause of his injuries.
OL,12,FCCTV showed Joyce entering Darren's
OL,13,Fhome at 4.55pm on the day of his
OL,14,Fdeath, and then leaving an hour and a
OL,15,Fhalf later carrying a television in a
OL,16,Fbag.
OL,18,FNo-one else was seen entering or
OL,19,Fleaving the house until Darren's body
OL,20,Fwas found the next day.
