OL,3,CThief guilty of murdering 'kind' man
OL,4,Cwho died in house fire
OL,6,FAfter a trial at Leeds Crown Court,
OL,7,FJoyce was found guilty of murder and
OL,8,Ftheft and will be sentenced on
OL,9,FWednesday 12 November.
OL,11,FA family statement from Darren Leach's
OL,12,Fsiblings read: "William Joyce
OL,13,Fneedlessly murdered our brother Darren
OL,14,FLeach on the 18th March this year,
OL,15,Finside his own home knowing Darren was
OL,16,Fno match for Joyce and therefore
OL,17,Funable to stand up and defend himself
OL,18,Fagainst William Joyce's vicious fatal
OL,19,Fattack.
