OL,3,CThief guilty of murdering 'kind' man
OL,4,Cwho died in house fire
OL,6,F"We all are extremely happy with the
OL,7,Fjury coming to a unanimous decision
OL,8,Fand finding William Joyce guilty of
OL,9,Fmurdering Darren Leach."
OL,11,FIt continued: "Despite the verdict, we
OL,12,Fare still left with the pain and
OL,13,Fheartache of Darren's death, knowing
OL,14,Fwe will never see him again and Darren
OL,15,Fwill never get to see his children and
OL,16,Fgrandchildren grow up.
OL,18,F"Darren was a kind and thoughtful man
OL,19,Fwho lost his way through tragedy,
OL,20,Flosing our mother in 2007. Darren has
OL,21,Fnow got the justice he deserves."
